Altough the 3 algorithms seemed to give the desired result in this case, but it is clearly not advised to use the above 3 algorithms in case of negatively
weighted, directed graphs.
The optimal solution in this case would be is to use an algorithm named, "Bellman Ford Algorithm".

Links referred for Bellman Ford:
https://www.cs.cmu.edu/afs/cs/academic/class/15210-f11/www/lectures/10/lecture10.pdf
